{"id": "1481908605748777163", "channel_id": "1481908605748777163", "type": 0, "author_id": "1430361164029624460", "author_name": "salami_87", "author_bot": false, "content": "When using Vortice’s Overexalt, it grants 5 charges that should allow a double activation of Pursuit. However, the Vortice Posse, which is supposed to trigger the Vórtice! Shell! Pursuit, only activates the effect once when it should activate twice. Otherwise, there would be no reason for one of the 5 charges granted by the Overexalt to be consumed after using the Posse.", "timestamp": "2026-03-13T06:55:44.141000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Winkle_frustrated", "emoji_id": "1468257899330539774", "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1481908606516596786", "filename": "Screenrecorder-2026-03-13-01-40-08-4750.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 8042968, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1481908605748777163/1481908606516596786/Screenrecorder-2026-03-13-01-40-08-4750.mp4?ex=69fb8eb0&is=69fa3d30&hm=1183b4d21b34dbc743ca0bf499b998d78012484d4d59bde399c2314268bfca21&"}, {"id": "1481908607623630928", "filename": "IMG_20260313_014144.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 42482, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1481908605748777163/1481908607623630928/IMG_20260313_014144.jpg?ex=69fb8eb0&is=69fa3d30&hm=49c09c1363487b183bf46869cdc0d6bf9302ca49513e771fb4d6517bdcbac4d9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1481908605748777163", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Resolved」Vortice Posse bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1481853610856943758", "channel_id": "1481853610856943758", "type": 0, "author_id": "212031841786527764", "author_name": "chinkeeyong", "author_bot": false, "content": "Previously, when an awakener deals damage via poison or poison triggers, it was reflected in the damage breakdown screen at the end of the stage.\n\nThis no longer seems to be the case. You can see that I have over 20k poison in this clear but none of this damage is shown in the statistics screen.\n\nPlease fix this so i can continue spreading propaganda about why poison units are powerful <:Doll_Wait:1468259092459032606>", "timestamp": "2026-03-13T03:17:12.337000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1481853611339284541", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-03-13_110844.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2403132, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1481853610856943758/1481853611339284541/Screenshot_2026-03-13_110844.png?ex=69fb5b78&is=69fa09f8&hm=6ac400c5c92a3bd74828d0ad3c1b8e74a39fbee6243ff823525cab5979954b25&"}, {"id": "1481853611980882040", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-03-13_111339.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 681219, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1481853610856943758/1481853611980882040/Screenshot_2026-03-13_111339.png?ex=69fb5b78&is=69fa09f8&hm=60c9b3f22623b8533a7f58e7f4025a319cbad04afd5c7ffb3f547479265cf33d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1481853610856943758", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Poison no longer shown in damage statistics", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1481848729416765471", "channel_id": "1481848729416765471", "type": 0, "author_id": "476427200015368193", "author_name": "qingming6054", "author_bot": false, "content": "80级10灵塑的莫丝，涡流弹固定伤害应为25740（与卡面所示数值相同）\n=220攻击力 * 1.3灵塑攻击力加成 * 30涡流弹倍率 * （1+200%灵塑涡流弹伤害加成）\n但如视频所示，对融灾5-5第一波小怪，实际造成伤害为4859\n\n该莫丝精通为108，应造成生命上限1.04%的额外伤害，\n涡流弹对54708生命值的小怪应造成569额外伤害\n去除该部分后，剩余伤害 = 4859-569 = 4290\n刚好是正常值25740的1/6\n\n另，该现象在融灾1-5也可复现，\n涡流弹造成4807伤害，目标血量49668，额外伤害应为517\n因此固定伤害依然 = 4807 - 517 = 4290\n\n该情况极大概率可复现，但不是100%，具体条件未测出\n<@1131790839291596841>", "timestamp": "2026-03-13T02:57:48.511000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-13T03:05:38.740000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1481848730444501202", "filename": "84f628a402e0a7e2e5d91cb919570004.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 3539096, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1481848729416765471/1481848730444501202/84f628a402e0a7e2e5d91cb919570004.mp4?ex=69fb56ec&is=69fa056c&hm=ced85376cb4169ee03d1280c3b2d6d49b6f91bc68b3ab56be02ca1d32f0218dc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1481848729416765471", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已解决」莫丝涡流弹伤害异常", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
